# Реестр компонентов

## UI-компоненты (app/components/UI/)

| Компонент | Пропсы | Emits | Варианты |
|-----------|--------|-------|----------|
| MyBtn | type!, disabled?, isActive?, className?, styles?, variant? | click | base, primary, secondary |
| MyInput | modelValue?, placeholder?, disabled?, required?, variant?, isActive?, className?, styles?, type? | update:modelValue | base, primary, secondary |
| MySearch | className?, styles?, variant?, disabled? | — | base, primary, secondary |
| MySelect | className?, styles?, variant?, disabled? | — | base, primary, secondary |
| MySelectOption | className?, styles?, variant? | — | base, primary, secondary |
| MyCheckboxInput | disabled?, className?, styles?, variant?, checked? | change | base, primary, secondary |
| MyRadioInput | className?, styles?, variant?, disabled? | change | base, primary, secondary |
| MyFileInput | disabled?, styles?, className?, variant?, isActive? | update:modelValue | base, primary, secondary |
| MyIcon | id?, href?, className?, variant?, disabled?, isActive?, styles? | — | base, primary, secondary |
| MyLink | href?, target?, variant?, className?, styles?, isActive?, disabled? | — | base, primary, secondary |
| MyNavLink | to?, variant?, className?, styles?, isActive?, disabled? | — | base, primary, secondary |
| MyPagination | className?, styles?, variant?, disabled? | click | base, primary, secondary |

`!` = обязательный, `?` = опциональный.

Каждый UI-компонент имеет `_config.scss` с SCSS map вариантов. Стили генерируются через `@each`.

## Layout-компоненты (app/components/Layout/)

| Компонент | Пропсы | Slots |
|-----------|--------|-------|
| AppHeader | — | logo, actions |
| AppFooter | — | default |

## State-компоненты (app/components/State/)

| Компонент | Пропсы | Emits |
|-----------|--------|-------|
| AppLoading | variant?("spinner"\|"skeleton"\|"dots"), size?(32) | — |
| AppError | title!, message?, retryable? | retry |
| AppEmpty | title!, message?, icon? | — |
